Package org.apache.hadoop.hbase.backup.master

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BackupLogCleaner
    Implementation of a log cleaner that checks if a log is still scheduled for incremental backup before deleting it when its TTL is over.
    LogRollMasterProcedureManager
    Master procedure manager for coordinated cluster-wide WAL roll operation, which is run during backup operation, see MasterProcedureManager and RegionServerProcedureManager
